	        </div>
	    </div>
	</div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
	    <div class="card profile-card-2" style="background-image: url('https://i.pinimg.com/originals/df/7f/4c/df7f4c51df5edae3e9bf78fef81f4000.jpg');">
	        <div class="card-img-block">
	            <img class="img-fluid" src="https://townsquare.media/site/103/files/2014/04/84010602-630x450.jpg?w=980&q=75" alt="Card image cap" style="width: 150px;height: 150px;border-radius: 50%;display: block;margin: 15px auto 0;">
	        </div>
	        <div class="card-body pt-5">
	            <h5 class="card-title" style="text-align:center;">Lend Books</h5>
	            <p class="card-text">Got some books on your shelf that are of no more use to you. Why not sell them on <strong>KitabBuddy</strong>?<br>Get the best price for your books and help someone else need.<strong>What are you waiting for!</strong></p>
