	        </div>
	    </div>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4">
	    <div class="card profile-card-2" style="background-image: url('http://getwallpapers.com/wallpaper/full/6/4/7/1392811-gorgerous-simple-background-pictures-1920x1080-htc.jpg');">
