	            <img class="img-fluid" src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/a3/1b/1d/a31b1d35380af24948f54b42346225f6.png" alt="Card image cap" style="width: 150px;height: 150px;border-radius: 50%;display: block;margin: 15px auto 0;">
	        </div>
	        <div class="card-body pt-5">
	            <h5 class="card-title">About Us</h5>
	            <p class="card-text"><strong>KitabBuddy</strong> serves the platform for the ones in need of books but are not able to pay its hefty market price, and for the ones who have old books stacking up in their shelves and want to sell it.<br>Know more about us, our future vision and our mission.</p>
	            <div style="text-align:center"><a href="#" class="btn btn-info stretched-link">More About Us</a></div>
	        </div>
	    </div>
	</div>
</div>
</div>

		
